---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import PageMeta from '../components/PageMeta.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Adoption"
  description="Who is implementing PDTF, what they have built, and the public evidence the framework works in practice."
  page="adoption"
  section="adoption"
>
<PageMeta category="Section overview" variant="brand" updated="Updated 2026-05-14" />

      <h1>Adoption</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        The market evidence. Member implementations using the schemas in production,
        the Sandbox pilots stress-testing the trust framework, the Moverly + OPDA
        Smart Data Challenge prize win, and HM Land Registry's 200+ council Local Land
        Charges migration — all in one place.
      </p>

      <h2 id="pilots">Pilots &amp; implementations</h2>
      <p>Live deployments of PDTF schemas in industry products.</p>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <a class="card" href="/pages/50-adoption-overview.html">
          <div class="pill pill--brand">Start here</div>
          <h3>Adoption overview</h3>
          <p>Headline numbers, what counts as adoption, and the public evidence map.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="/pages/51-member-implementations.html">
          <div class="pill pill--info">Built</div>
          <h3>Member implementations</h3>
          <p>Connells Digital Sale Ready · Moverly · OnTheMarket · Homely · Sprift · Groundsure — what each has built.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="/pages/54-sandbox-pilots.html">
          <div class="pill pill--info">Built</div>
          <h3>Sandbox pilots</h3>
          <p>What the CLC + OPDA + Raidiam Sandbox is testing in 2026 — certified data sources, accredited service providers, consent &amp; liability models.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <h2 id="programmes">Programmes</h2>
      <p>Government-backed programmes that have validated PDTF-aligned approaches.</p>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <a class="card" href="/pages/52-smart-data-challenge.html">
          <div class="pill pill--info">Built</div>
          <h3>Smart Data Challenge 2025</h3>
          <p>DBT-sponsored open call. Moverly + OPDA entry won the SDCP Innovators prize. Property Pack + Digital ID prize entries archived.</p>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="/pages/53-hmlr-llc.html">
          <div class="pill pill--info">Built</div>
          <h3>HMLR Local Land Charges</h3>
          <p>200+ councils migrated to the national HMLR-run digital register. Quarterly "gold status" ratings for register quality.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
</Layout>
